===Intransitive verb===
[[Category:English intransitive verbs]]
'''to shy''', '''shies''', '''shied'''; usually '''to shy away from'''

#to [[avoid]] due to timidness or caution
#:''I '''shy away from''' investment opportunities I don't understand.''

